{"tid":850031,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"讀唔到大學個班人打夠飛機未？","createTime":"2018-10-06T06:53:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-06T10:08:53.000Z","uid":200186,"like":39,"dislike":10,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"082d9172a557f18083c61529293ad5713886b7a6","tid":850031,"uid":200186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:53:08.000Z","msg":"根本自己就係冇料讀大學，自己廢又成撚日係到講埋哂啲&rdquo;依家啲大學生死讀書&rdquo;, &ldquo;識人好過識字&rdquo;呢啲說話去掩飾自己太過垃圾嘅事實。講真依家香港啲大學入學門檻越尼越低，咁都冇八大學位仲好意思覺得所有大學生都高分低能？最好笑係成撚日攞啲名人尼打飛機，話咩李嘉誠冇讀過大學都係全港首富，又話Steve jobs都冇讀大學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 你睇下自己幾多斤兩先啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 好意思將自己同李嘉誠類比？人地係有料讀大學但自己揀唔讀，你地係根本冇料讀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有啲即使升唔到大學都願意岀尼學做野或者學其他技能，但有啲就好似我上述講個啲咁，淨係識打飛機自我感覺良好<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 醒未？"},{"pid":"75aeb4f5ab467c48ba8b46b42a6be4b85c5f7988","tid":850031,"uid":90,"like":27,"dislike":0,"score":27,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T06:59:16.000Z","msg":"希望ching下次可以識用隔行"},{"pid":"99a5dc9eff91fd3c32340fa9d4315d479cb74b85","tid":850031,"uid":128600,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:01:12.000Z","msg":"我冇料讀大學。。。。<br />\n但我靠大學生供養我"},{"pid":"1473263f71479254dfad9279d5fdfd48ed15b7b5","tid":850031,"uid":2419,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:01:23.000Z","msg":"尼你老母"},{"pid":"70c7cfe2a002f9c967c508858dbb36e6fea49a29","tid":850031,"uid":85564,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:07:02.000Z","msg":"其實依家已經冇人唱呢支歌仔<br />\n<br />\n中伏個啲都已經中哂伏<br />\n<br />\n收哂皮"},{"pid":"57dbf71ae2d1f990a09e0ff54d47a13dd54c42b9","tid":850031,"uid":37942,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:08:33.000Z","msg":"講真哂錢"},{"pid":"2340d692ca3efedcedd0b16318e79f48e3b5415b","tid":850031,"uid":29606,"like":4,"dislike":5,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-06T07:08